{"tid":249142,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"大背囊hand carry","createTime":"2017-05-19T05:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T08:57:42.000Z","uid":28001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f497d375a3a80a7e8c7ce799e9bba6103db93a6e","tid":249142,"uid":28001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:51:49.000Z","msg":"嚟緊去日本打算帶個F-stop tilopa去<br />\n個尺寸係59.7*35.6*30.5cm<br />\n<br />\n重量有機會會over 10kg <br />\n(2個相機body, 4支鏡, notebook, 尿袋, 衫, gimbal, 雜物等等)<br />\n腳架就應該會寄倉.<br />\n<br />\n搭因航， 頭先check咗無論重量同size都過晒hand carry<br />\n<br />\n因航hand carry規定: 56*36*23cm 7KG<br />\n我個case : <span style=\"color: red;\">59.7</span>*35.6*<span style=\"color: red;\">30.5cm</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">10KG</span><br />\n<br />\n因為係背囊，所以如果同佢拗我壓到佢規定個range應該ok?<br />\n如果重量方面 我應該可以掉多3KG落喼嘅(但最好唔好，電池最重但唔可以寄倉，鏡頭寄倉又驚地勤大佬屌爆晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n我想問下有無巴絲打有無經驗 呢類大背囊會唔會被逼寄倉?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79066233ae86ac760f171b8e48533232dfd5e2c7","tid":249142,"uid":28001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T07:27:51.000Z","msg":"pish <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"defde50f912160d1b9e004a361a1391891cd9f24","tid":249142,"uid":8681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T07:29:15.000Z","msg":"你個背囊好似唔係超好多咋喎 除非執正黎做 可能都上到"},{"pid":"89f60135c83d173390a391d526b07b9288c477c6","tid":249142,"uid":28001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T07:32:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個背囊好似唔係超好多咋喎 除非執正黎做 可能都上到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實感覺唔係超好多，我係怕佢會執正嚟做<br />\n所以想問下巴絲打有冇經驗，多唔多呢啲case?<br />\n第一次hand carry大背囊上機。一般都係細背囊。無呢方面經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58a3190875a4bed9dfcc856681779a259b5a2a3","tid":249142,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T07:33:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個背囊好似唔係超好多咋喎 除非執正黎做 可能都上到</blockquote><br />\n佢兩邊都超喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cecbf90038072bbe8a82441d470c5234f1e5f3a","tid":249142,"uid":8681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T07:46:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你個背囊好似唔係超好多咋喎 除非執正黎做 可能都上到</blockquote><br />\n佢兩邊都超喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n3cm目測都睇到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e566ba857383e6fd2808f0c7ec065e96012997","tid":249142,"uid":8681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T07:49:29.000Z","msg":"你係咪會裝到爆晒人地一睇就知超晒標?"},{"pid":"39ff4940c0aed46084613aefb66f396b13d88bb7","tid":249142,"uid":28001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:00:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪會裝到爆晒人地一睇就知超晒標?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n爆就唔會爆。我會將部分放落gip<br />\n問題係。個背囊有相機內膽。會挺到個背囊好漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a66fda7493b64c75b9b16ebd69f37ec55bbb03","tid":249142,"uid":38665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:56:51.000Z","msg":"而家地勤多數會過磅，超左一定要你寄倉"},{"pid":"4e74be671d7c5b262d6947ebb45f94030eac536a","tid":249142,"uid":28001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:57:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家地勤多數會過磅，超左一定要你寄倉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打！ 即係我keep under 7KG應該可以?"}]}